SUPLINF.P:
USDA received 117 comments on the NSLP snacks proposal in the 2023 rule, including 111 unique comments. Of these, 58 supported the proposal, 3 were opposed, and 56 were mixed. State agencies, advocacy groups, dietitians, and individuals submitted comments in response to this proposal. In addition, USDA received five comments in response to the 2020 proposal to revise the definition of 
Child;
 all five respondents supported the proposed change.

